          "intermittent back pain",
          "back pain",
          "increased urine output",
          "no recent illness",
          "no fever",
          "recurrent strep infections",
          "strep infections"
        ]
      },
      {
        "heading": "O",
        "section_value": "Physical exam reveals no tenderness to palpation of the back, no cervical lymphadenopathy, and clear lung sounds. Vital signs are within normal limits. Examination of the throat reveals no erythema or swelling, and the tonsils are midline.",
        "medical_concepts": [
